content: Here's the info: I have Netflix, Hulu, Amazon Prime Video, Disney+, HBO Max, and Apple TV+. On Netflix, I've been watching "Schitt's Creek" with my girlfriend. On Hulu, I'm keeping up with "The Good Place" and "Brooklyn Nine-Nine". On Amazon Prime, I just finished binge-watching "The Expanse" - what a ride! On Disney+, I've been enjoying "The Mandalorian" and some old childhood favorites. On HBO Max, I just started watching "Game of Thrones" from the beginning. And on Apple TV+, I've been enjoying Oprah's book club series and "Little America".
